	* GenericFunctions: latest changes from Joe Boudreau
	* Matrix: cleanup for -Wextra

2012-05-11 Lynn Garren <garren@fnal.gov>

	* Vector, Evaluator, Random, Geometry: use explicit std:: with math functions

